<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 22:05:12 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“另一种恐惧”：10 月 7 日之后阿拉伯人和犹太人共存的脆弱性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-19/ty-article/.highlight/a-different-kind-of-fear-the-fragility-of-arab-jewish-coexistence-after-october-7/0000018b-e8a3-d32d-abdb-eee3db6e0000</link><description>加沙战争已经过去六周了，对 2021 年 5 月犹太和阿拉伯公民之间骚乱的报复并未实现。这片黑暗中唯一的一丝善意的背后是什么？</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 21:21:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-19/ty-article/.highlight/a-different-kind-of-fear-the-fragility-of-arab-jewish-coexistence-after-october-7/0000018b-e8a3-d32d-abdb-eee3db6e0000</guid></item><item><title>纽约市长指责教授在城市校园里营造了针对犹太人的仇恨氛围</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/new-york-mayor-blames-professors-for-hateful-atmosphere-against-jews-on-city-campuses/0000018b-e94b-d36e-a3cb-f95f9e6c0000</link><description>市长埃里克·亚当斯 (Eric Adams) 在曼哈顿中央犹太教堂告诉会众，校园已“成为仇恨的避风港”</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 20:59:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/new-york-mayor-blames-professors-for-hateful-atmosphere-against-jews-on-city-campuses/0000018b-e94b-d36e-a3cb-f95f9e6c0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日，以色列军队公布了加沙 Al-Shifa 医院内人质的录像</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/israeli-army-releases-footage-of-hostages-inside-gazas-al-shifa-hospital-on-oct-7/0000018b-e93d-d36e-a3cb-f97f56bb0000</link><description>此外，以色列军方发言人丹尼尔·哈加里表示，被绑架并带入加沙地带的士兵诺亚·马西亚诺先被带到Al-Shifa医院附近的一处藏身处公寓，随后又被带入医院，并在那里被谋杀。病理报告证实</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 20:29:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/israeli-army-releases-footage-of-hostages-inside-gazas-al-shifa-hospital-on-oct-7/0000018b-e93d-d36e-a3cb-f97f56bb0000</guid></item><item><title>将加沙交给驻加沙的多国部队只是一个幻想</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/multinational-force-just-a-bypass-around-the-palestinian-authority/0000018b-e8ae-d6b8-a5ab-ecee5d580000</link><description>战争结束后，阿拉伯国家拒绝向加沙派遣军队，而内塔尼亚胡则排除了巴勒斯坦权力机构控制该地区的可能性。但由非阿拉伯多国部队掌权的想法毫无意义</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 20:06:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/multinational-force-just-a-bypass-around-the-palestinian-authority/0000018b-e8ae-d6b8-a5ab-ecee5d580000</guid></item><item><title>前以色列外交官呼吁建立国际联盟，其国民被哈马斯扣为人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/ex-israeli-diplomats-call-for-an-intl-coalition-whose-nationals-are-held-hostage-by-hamas/0000018b-e915-d36e-a3cb-f9571b900000</link><description>该组织的代表和以色列退休大使呼吁联合国任命一名人质问题特别代表，要求红十字会在与哈马斯打交道时更加自信</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 19:57:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/ex-israeli-diplomats-call-for-an-intl-coalition-whose-nationals-are-held-hostage-by-hamas/0000018b-e915-d36e-a3cb-f9571b900000</guid></item><item><title>美国相信内塔尼亚胡最终将支持控制加沙的巴勒斯坦权力机构</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/u-s-believes-netanyahu-will-eventually-support-palestinian-authority-controlling-gaza/0000018b-e88a-d6b8-a5ab-ecea67b10000</link><description>美国官员认为，如果巴勒斯坦权力机构同意停止在国际机构中针对以色列的行动，并结束其在以色列监狱中为被定罪的杀人犯提供极具争议的支付制度，那么耶路撒冷对巴勒斯坦权力机构的态度将会软化。</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 19:22:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/u-s-believes-netanyahu-will-eventually-support-palestinian-authority-controlling-gaza/0000018b-e88a-d6b8-a5ab-ecea67b10000</guid></item><item><title>美国敦促以色列推迟对加沙南部的袭击，直到北部流离失所的巴勒斯坦人得到解决</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/u-s-presses-to-delay-south-gaza-strikes-until-displaced-palestinians-are-accounted-for/0000018b-e8bd-d6b8-a5ab-ecfff6b10000</link><description>国家安全顾问乔恩·费纳表示，人们“真正担心”以色列将行动转移到南部，在以色列的敦促下，那里有数十万人逃离</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 19:09:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/u-s-presses-to-delay-south-gaza-strikes-until-displaced-palestinians-are-accounted-for/0000018b-e8bd-d6b8-a5ab-ecfff6b10000</guid></item><item><title>史前澳大利亚人将野狗与家人一起埋葬在空中</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-11-19/ty-article/prehistoric-australians-buried-their-dingoes-in-the-sky-with-people/0000018b-e82d-d570-a7cf-fa7d9be60000</link><description>澳大利亚原住民终生饲养野狗，可能是几代人，这与该岛殖民时代野生小狗袭击的报道形成鲜明对比</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 16:25:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-11-19/ty-article/prehistoric-australians-buried-their-dingoes-in-the-sky-with-people/0000018b-e82d-d570-a7cf-fa7d9be60000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的福音派恋情无助于削弱美国对以色列的支持</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/young-americans-dont-support-israel-netanyahus-affair-with-evangelicals-isnt-helping/0000018b-e7c1-d05f-a5eb-e7e15af30000</link><description>随着年轻的美国选民越来越倾向于支持巴勒斯坦人而不是以色列，一个群体仍然坚定地支持犹太国家 — — 这只会加剧以色列和民主党之间的分裂</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 16:02:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/young-americans-dont-support-israel-netanyahus-affair-with-evangelicals-isnt-helping/0000018b-e7c1-d05f-a5eb-e7e15af30000</guid></item><item><title>加拿大性侵犯中心主任因质疑哈马斯强奸以色列妇女的说法而被解雇</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/americas/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/head-of-canadian-sexual-assault-center-fired-for-questioning-accounts-of-hamas-rapes/0000018b-e7f8-d05f-a5eb-e7f8d6c80000</link><description>阿尔伯塔大学性侵犯中心主任萨曼莎·皮尔森签署了一封信，提到“反复且未经证实的指控巴勒斯坦人犯有性暴力罪”</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 15:25:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/americas/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/head-of-canadian-sexual-assault-center-fired-for-questioning-accounts-of-hamas-rapes/0000018b-e7f8-d05f-a5eb-e7f8d6c80000</guid></item><item><title>东耶路撒冷记者因涉嫌煽动和鼓励恐怖主义而被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/east-jlem-journalist-arrested-on-suspicion-of-incitement-and-encouraging-terrorism/0000018b-e7f3-d05f-a5eb-e7f375eb0000</link><description>NBC 的自由撰稿人记者 Marwat Al-Azza 据称嘲笑了 10 月 7 日加沙边境社区一名以色列老年妇女被绑架的事件。治安法院下令将她的拘留期限延长四天</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 15:11:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/east-jlem-journalist-arrested-on-suspicion-of-incitement-and-encouraging-terrorism/0000018b-e7f3-d05f-a5eb-e7f375eb0000</guid></item><item><title>安全官员：64岁以色列人质在加沙被杀害，绑匪逃离以色列国防军</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/security-officials-64-year-old-hostage-was-murdered-as-kidnappers-fled-from-idf-forces/0000018b-e7d2-d05f-a5eb-e7f2966f0000</link><description>以色列军队在希法医院附近发现了韦斯的尸体，并于上周将其送回以色列。 10月7日，贝埃里基布兹居民韦斯被绑架到加沙，她的丈夫什穆里克被谋杀</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 14:54:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/security-officials-64-year-old-hostage-was-murdered-as-kidnappers-fled-from-idf-forces/0000018b-e7d2-d05f-a5eb-e7f2966f0000</guid></item><item><title>基地组织俘虏了我。以色列如何释放哈马斯扣押的人质？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-19/ty-article-opinion/.premium/al-qaeda-held-me-captive-what-must-israel-do-to-free-the-hostages-held-by-hamas/0000018b-e692-d867-abab-f7b6581e0000</link><description>就像哈马斯将 10 月 7 日对以色列的袭击命名为阿克萨洪水行动一样，我的基地组织绑架者也将自己视为改变全球的灾难的一部分，而哈马斯人质面临的危险每时每刻都在加剧。这是我要告诉以色列决策者的话</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 13:58:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-19/ty-article-opinion/.premium/al-qaeda-held-me-captive-what-must-israel-do-to-free-the-hostages-held-by-hamas/0000018b-e692-d867-abab-f7b6581e0000</guid></item><item><title>随着法国反犹太主义的高涨，一些犹太人采取新措施来隐藏他们的宗教信仰</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/as-antisemitism-spikes-in-france-some-jews-adopt-new-measures-to-hide-their-religion/0000018b-e73c-d867-abab-f7bc1d100000</link><description>当法国犹太人试图通过移除门框上的门柱等方式保持低调时，社区领袖建议不要“让反犹太主义者觉得他们已经取得了一些成功”，一位大屠杀幸存者告诉巴黎的年轻犹太人：“你应该这样做”。不要害怕&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 13:54:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/as-antisemitism-spikes-in-france-some-jews-adopt-new-measures-to-hide-their-religion/0000018b-e73c-d867-abab-f7bc1d100000</guid></item><item><title>约旦河西岸成为以色列战争中令人不安的第三条战线</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/the-west-bank-emerges-as-a-third-and-troubling-front-in-israels-war/0000018b-e764-df9a-ab8b-ffeccb7f0000</link><description>以色列可以继续打着“追捕哈马斯”的旗号镇压加沙，打着“打击恐怖主义”的口号推平约旦河西岸，但我们必须明白，每发生一次死亡，新一代巴勒斯坦年轻人就会加入到反对以色列的斗争中。</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 12:18:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/the-west-bank-emerges-as-a-third-and-troubling-front-in-israels-war/0000018b-e764-df9a-ab8b-ffeccb7f0000</guid></item><item><title>散居海外的犹太人成为以色列行为的人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article-opinion/.premium/diaspora-jews-are-hostages-to-israels-behavior/0000018b-e420-d867-abab-f5a4592d0000</link><description>散居海外的犹太人经历了惨痛的教训，无论他们的派别或政治立场如何，他们都会成为严厉批评以色列行为的出气筒，煽动行为会演变成反犹太主义。现在是以色列至少承认这一现实的时候了</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 08:32:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article-opinion/.premium/diaspora-jews-are-hostages-to-israels-behavior/0000018b-e420-d867-abab-f5a4592d0000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔表示，以色列与哈马斯人质协议面临的挑战“只是后勤方面的”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/negotiations-over-hostage-release-held-up-as-israel-waits-for-hamas/0000018b-e69d-dffa-adef-e69d32ea0000</link><description>卡塔尔总理阿勒萨尼表示，达成协议之前的剩余挑战“只是实际和后勤方面的挑战”。几小时前，《华盛顿邮报》报道称，双方已达成一项临时协议，以释放数十名妇女和儿童，以换取暂停五天的战斗。到达</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 08:32:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/negotiations-over-hostage-release-held-up-as-israel-waits-for-hamas/0000018b-e69d-dffa-adef-e69d32ea0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军展示了加沙希法医院内人质的镜头，称以色列士兵被带到那里并被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article-live/biden-says-gaza-and-west-bank-should-be-ruled-by-renewed-pa/0000018b-e568-dffa-adef-e76822250000</link><description>以色列国防军在周六宣布 8 人死亡后，又公布了 5 名阵亡士兵的名字 ■ 以色列安全内阁批准燃料进入加沙 ■ 也门胡塞武装劫持了以色列拥有的货船 ■ 卡塔尔总理称人质协议面临的挑战“非常小” ■ 至少 1,200 名平民自 10 月 7 日以来，还有士兵被杀； 236 名人质在加沙被扣押 ■ 哈马斯控制的卫生部：12,300 人死亡</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 04:01:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article-live/biden-says-gaza-and-west-bank-should-be-ruled-by-renewed-pa/0000018b-e568-dffa-adef-e76822250000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和世界必须认清反犹太主义者的本质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-and-the-world-must-recognize-antisemites-for-what-they-are/0000018b-e3be-d867-abab-f7be96930000</link><description>让我们考虑一下在自诩为人文自由主义者中变得如此流行的口号：从河流到海洋，巴勒斯坦将是自由的。实际上免费什么？</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 00:34:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-and-the-world-must-recognize-antisemites-for-what-they-are/0000018b-e3be-d867-abab-f7be96930000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-19/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-e4e9-dffa-adef-e6e955bf0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 00:11:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-19/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-e4e9-dffa-adef-e6e955bf0000</guid></item></channel></rss>